<ab facs="#facs_352_r1l30"><expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tün was vvir <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vr </del> das vns cʒeıtlıch </ab>
